citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:04 am on May 6,
2021.
Inspectors arrived at the facility at 11:04 am and called licensee. The licensee stated she was not on premises but could
be available in one hour. After waiting one hour at 12:04 pm inspectors again called licensee. The licensee stated she
would not be able to make it to the facility this afternoon. The inspectors then left the premises.
Additional Inspectors:
TYLER FIELDS, VETERINARY MEDICAL OFFICEREnd Section
